org.ndeftools.externaltype
Class AndroidApplicationRecord

java.lang.Object
  org.ndeftools.Record
      org.ndeftools.externaltype.ExternalTypeRecord
          org.ndeftools.externaltype.AndroidApplicationRecord

public class AndroidApplicationRecord
extends ExternalTypeRecord

Android Application Record. This is an Android-specific record type which attempts to launch the application specified by the package name. If no such application exists on the device, Google Play is launched at the corresponding application page.

Author:
Thomas Rorvik Skjolberg (skjolber@gmail.com)
